{"tid":999598,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「金融巨鱷」索羅斯抨擊習近平 用AI鎮壓民主","createTime":"2019-01-28T23:28:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-31T13:13:14.000Z","uid":141151,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fee9c71e8dbc2827650ab52eebd9aaf6c8e0cd43","tid":999598,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T23:28:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>「金融巨鱷」索羅斯抨擊習近平 用AI鎮壓民主</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6809/3613627\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6809%2F3613627&d=RH6Ab9G4Smx3Ukb%2FUx9OAEjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=98bb79bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6809/3613627</a><br />\n<br />\n「金融巨鱷」索羅斯示警，中國獨裁政權運用人工智慧（AI）鎮壓民眾，有「致命危險」，中國領導人習近平是民主最危險的敵人。<br />\n<br />\n今年88歲的索羅斯在達沃斯世界經濟論壇（WEF）上表示：<span style=\"color: red;\">「運用AI開發出來的控制設備，讓集權政府獲得優勢，危及開放社會。中國並非世界唯一專制政權，但它無疑是最富裕、最強大的政權，也是機器學習和人工智慧領域最先進的國家。」</span><br />\n<br />\n索羅斯指出，中國正在研發集中化的資料庫，透過演算法決定哪些人對其一黨獨大的體制造成威脅。這套所謂的「社會信用系統」雖然尚未全面上路，但「將會以歷史上前所未見的方式，將個人的命運置於獨裁黨國之下。」"},{"pid":"6181941cd9d137fb73bc2402bd7ad552dc49d7db","tid":999598,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T23:29:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"671fd8984c70002e43b0bd1f581549b5e293d1e5","tid":999598,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T23:35:08.000Z","msg":"秦始皇差唔多"},{"pid":"dfefe6c9c2478328caea2c5fdcd24c75ed618dba","tid":999598,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"671fd8984c70002e43b0bd1f581549b5e293d1e5","tid":999598,"uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T23:35:08.000Z","msg":"秦始皇差唔多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T00:05:15.000Z","msg":"<im